    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>3D密室逃脱：中式房间</strong>是一款中国风的密室逃脱游戏。玩家将置身于多个充满神秘与挑战的中式场景中，逐步探索和解开隐藏的谜题。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>东方禅意之美</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个场景都向中国传统禅宗美学致敬，安静的光影、简洁的线条、柔和的色调，为解谜增添了宁静与专注。我们希望通过视觉传达出禅意氛围，让玩家置身于宁静的古代中式庭院中，感受独特的文化韵味。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精美的3D画面</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细腻的纹理、柔和的光影以及逼真的物理效果，为玩家带来视觉享受，同时增强谜题探索的沉浸感。场景设计精雕细琢，从石刻细节到窗棂雕花，仿佛让人身临其境，置身于真实的中国古代世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>难度适中的谜题设计</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中设计了一系列经典的谜题和小游戏，难度适中，既不会过于简单也不会让人束手无策。玩家能在解谜过程中体验到成就感与探索的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
